    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/19/15595270/241eba6e4c00020975cf91170050f435_9084194203880038190.png",
                "id": "talent14248",
                "key": "Line Bayonet Thrust EX",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Line Bayonet Thrust EX"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: #FF9999\">Pyro DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Setelah penghitungan Skill ini selesai</span>: jika di Tanganmu terdapat <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Overcharged Ball</span>: <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Buang</span> 1 kartu dan memulihkan 1 poin HP Karaktermu yang menerima DMG terbesar.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/19/15595270/52cd1e5b70e7ea798b5a41cd9a51fbef_552773462184929887.png",
                "id": "talent12656",
                "key": "Short-Range Rapid Interdiction Fire",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Short-Range Rapid Interdiction Fire"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: #FF9999\">Pyro DMG</span> dan menciptakan <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Secondary Explosive Shells</span> di area lawan.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Secondary Explosive Shells</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status Pertempuran</span> </p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Setelah pemain di sisi ini bertukar Karakter:</span> mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #FF9999\">Pyro DMG</span> terhadap Karakter aktif baru yang ditukar.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Penggunaan: 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/19/15595270/a36c7a9c9512124baf0b482d8dc69912_2239144365157351645.png",
                "id": "talent78817",
                "key": "Ring of Bursting Grenades",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Ring of Bursting Grenades"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>[Pasif] <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Setelah Karakter lawan menerima DMG dari Reaksi Overloaded:</span> menciptakan 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Overcharged Ball</span>. (Sekali setiap Ronde)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/19/15595270/4b48c030ba601eab2fe4d2375057a617_5046272481651904750.png",
                "id": "talent98105",
                "key": "Vertical Force Coordination",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Vertical Force Coordination"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Kartu Peristiwa </span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Aksi Tempur</span>: mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #FF9999\">Pyro DMG</span> terhadap \"Karakter aktif\" musuh. <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Saat kartu ini dibuang</span>: mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #FF9999\">Pyro DMG</span> terhadap \"Karakter aktif\" musuh.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/19/15595270/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_9031440121052279577.png",
                "id": "talent75774",
                "key": "Overcharged Ball",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/19/15595270/5dca55a012526872199ffb25f0129241_246283369832926523.png",
                "title": "Overcharged Ball"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Pyro dan dapat memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini, target berganti ke Karakter selanjutnya secara paksa</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] yang mengakibatkan 1 poin Pyro DMG di akhir Ronde (Jumlah penggunaan sekali, maksimum 2 tumpukan)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/19/15595270/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_5661953543396295214.png",
                "id": "talent19675",
                "key": "Pyro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Pyro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Aksi Tempur</span></strong></p><p>Setelah kamu menyelesaikan 1 Aksi Tempur, selanjutnya adalah giliran lawanmu.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Memainkan 1 kartu dari tanganmu dengan aturan ini berarti Aksi Tempur, dan bukan Aksi Cepat.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Buang</span></strong></p><p>Gunakan efek Kartu Aksi atau Skill Karakter untuk membuang Kartu Aksi dari Tangan atau Dek-mu.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/19/15595270/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_7386611685428517269.png",
                "id": "talent4639",
